---
title: Glazed Chermoula Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt
description: A sweet honey glaze on chermoula-spiced chicken breast? We say yes please! Feast your eyes on this delectable dinner, with a colourful veggie-speckled couscous acting as a fluffy bed for all of that juicy, beefy goodness. All you need is a dollop of garlic yoghurt for a touch of tang!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
